'''''burárum''''' was an [[Entish]] sound or word issued by [[Treebeard]] when he spoke of [[Orcs]]. The word is described as a "deep rumbling noise like a discord on a great organ", signifying Treebeard's disgust at the thought of these creatures. It is glossed as an "Entish noise of disgust".<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 79</ref>

